text = "This section scans [color=#a6e3a1]YAML[/color] files in your selected template folder. folder can be selected with the [color=#fab387]locate template folder[/color] button below

by default the generated yaml files are stored in:
[color=#89dceb]C:\\ProgramData\\Archipelago\\Players\\Templates[/color]. 
if this folder is found it is set by default but feel free to change it.

[color=#f38ba8]if the templates folder does not exist in your achipelago_install/players folder you likely still need to generate it. you can do this by opening the archipelago launcher -> generate template options. running this command will also open the location where the templates have been generated[/color]"
